    "Html": "\r\n<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>Unfortunately, there is nothing I can do here. The issue is that the Infragistics control (which I cannot change) fails to raise the event in a way that is caught by the EventTrigger (which is developed by Microsoft, and which I cannot change).</p>\r\n<p>I recommend calling Infragistics support and reporting the issue to them. If I had to guess, I'd say that their event is not routed properly.</p>\r\n<p>Cheers,</p>\r\n<p>Laurent</p>\r\n",
